title: Carefully Reckless Replay - Protect Black Men
itunes:title: Carefully Reckless Replay - Protect Black Men
description:
It's the last Wednesday in Black History Month, so Carefully Reckless presents a replay of one of its most memorable episodes.


Calling all black men! This is a safe place for you. Black women, I hope you're ready to take some accountability as Jess gives her opinion on the controversial topic of male vulnerability in the black community. Let's talk, so we can heal!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
